    text="{= ${HostelModel>/CGST} > 0 &amp;&amp; ${HostelModel>/EffectiveGSTValue} > 0 ? 'CGST (' + (${HostelModel>/EffectiveGSTType} === 'CGST/SGST' ? ${HostelModel>/EffectiveGSTValue}  : ${HostelModel>/EffectiveGSTValue}) + '%)' : 'CGST'}"
